(417, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/04/improvements-to-wordpress-org/''>Improvements to WordPress.org</a> <span class="rss-date">4 abril 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">If you visit WordPress.org regularly you might have noticed some changes around the place. If you don’t, now’s the time to check them out! We’ve been working hard to improve the site to make it more useful to everyone, both developers and users, and we hope you like what we’ve done. New Theme and Plugin Directories [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://ma.tt/2015/04/start-with-the-result/''>Matt: Start With The Result </a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/going-behind-the-scenes-with-the-jetpack-team''>WPTavern: Going Behind the Scenes with the Jetpack Team</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://ma.tt/2015/04/john-oliver-meets-snowden/''>Matt: John Oliver meets Snowden</a></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
